{"title":"Cane Creek Giveaway in Support of Bikepacking Roots’ BIPOC Bike Adventure Grant!","link":"https://theradavist.com/cane-creek-giveaway-in-support-of-bikepacking-roots-bipoc-bike-adventure-grant/","date":1710431465000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BikepackingRootsBIPOCgiveaway.jpg?fit=1200,1080&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BikepackingRootsBIPOCgiveaway.jpg?w=1620&amp;quality=75 1620w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BikepackingRootsBIPOCgiveaway.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BikepackingRootsBIPOCgiveaway.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/BikepackingRootsBIPOCgiveaway.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Bikepacking Roots wants to thank its amazing supporters like you and its fabulous brand sponsors for <a href=\"https://secure.lglforms.com/form_engine/s/JOmeE-GBJumPia3KB-pR2w?mc_cid=2273eadd64&amp;mc_eid=0aa340040b\" target=\"_blank\">donating to the BIPIC Bike Adventure Grant</a>. The 501(c)(3)  non-profit is getting so close to its goal. But they still need to raise $3,000 more to make its BIPOC BikeAdventure Grant Program a reality this year so they’ve teamed up with Cane Creek to sweeten the deal!<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-12.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-12.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-12.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-12.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-12.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-11.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-11.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-11.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-11.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Mosaic-x-TPC-GT-2-45-Review-11.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>To help BPR get there, they are thrilled to announce another giveaway featuring Cane Creek Cycling Components! Based in the mountains of Western North Carolina, Cane Creek is employee owned and operated, and is a team of individuals looking to make your riding experience better. Cane Creek is giving away an eeSilk Stem and eeSilk+ Seatpost! This gravel giveaway is valued at over $500!</p>\n<p><strong>Every $25 donation will get you an entry into this giveaway which only runs until Sunday March 17th, so don’t wait!⁠</strong></p>\n<p>Donate at <a href=\"https://secure.lglforms.com/form_engine/s/JOmeE-GBJumPia3KB-pR2w?mc_cid=2273eadd64&amp;mc_eid=0aa340040b\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Roots</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cane-creek-giveaway-in-support-of-bikepacking-roots-bipoc-bike-adventure-grant/\">Cane Creek Giveaway in Support of Bikepacking Roots’ BIPOC Bike Adventure Grant!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"969ec270aaaa9db24c5b705a952204ca09daa17d70beb5ad98ab61009770450c","category":"Cycling"}